{"tid":1278992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Stand With Hong Kong at G20 全球報紙集合展","createTime":"2019-07-02T14:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T02:35:34.000Z","uid":63459,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"26f33a493dcf2fc5f00a03577c10677f297b457f","tid":1278992,"uid":63459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"我地今日起一連六日喺灣仔艺鵠藝術空間搞左個全球報紙集合展<br />\n<br />\n入面會展出6月27至29日於全球共十三個國家、十九份報章上刊登嘅公開信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾籌組佢地登得咁辛苦，我地當然要有啲實物同大家分享，要搵哂咁多份返香港亦都相當唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面仲有我地精心設計嘅場刊 (非賣品)，絕密從未公開嘅設計亦會係場刊入面出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以多多支持，上嚟睇嘅時候都要記得好好珍惜啲報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#freedomhk <br />\n#g20<br />\n#antielab<br />\n<br />\n日期: 2-7 Jul 2019<br />\n時間: 下午1點至8點 (如反應熱烈，開放時間有可能加長，詳情麻煩留意fb專頁同IG)<br />\n地址: Art and Culture Outreach｜艺鵠 （灣仔軒尼詩道365-367號富德樓6樓）<br />\nPage: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E5%8F%B0-Anti-ELAB-Global-Updates-330464637848950/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%258F%25B0-Anti-ELAB-Global-Updates-330464637848950%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=cd0aef7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E5%8F%B0-Anti-ELAB-Global-Updates-330464637848950/</a><br />\nEvent Link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/491966818243423/?event_time_id=491966821576756?ti=icl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F491966818243423%2F%3Fevent_time_id%3D491966821576756%3Fti%3Dicl&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=eba3ecd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/491966818243423/?event_time_id=491966821576756?ti=icl</a><br />\nOfficial IG: @hknoelab_exhibition <br />\nACO IG: @artandcultureoutreach<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/02/220940_6bdaad9076120c8e14e6078820256a15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F02%2F220940_6bdaad9076120c8e14e6078820256a15.png&h=da54eaab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝艺鵠贊助場地<br />\n展覽由 反送中國際資訊台及C&amp;G藝術單位合辦"},{"pid":"b934bb5b6e79c9bc30b3318cad4077c9ee029040","tid":1278992,"uid":63459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"立場訪問: <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B1%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B1%E7%B4%99%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E5%B1%95-%E7%9B%BC%E5%9C%A8%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%AD%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%97%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25B4%2599%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%25B1%2595-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%25B5%2590%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=910c4a2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25B4%2599%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%25B1%2595-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%259C%2598%2